am World]]\n| length14     = 3:38\n| title15      = Voulez-Vous\n| note15       = extended remix; 1979 US promo\n| length15     = 6:10\n}}\n{{tracklist\n| collapsed = yes\n| headline  = 2010 deluxe edition DVD\n| title1    = ''ABBA in Switzerland''\n| note1     = [[BBC]] television special\n| title2    = Chiquitita\n| note2     = [[Music for UNICEF Concert|Music for UNICEF]]\n| title3    = I Have a Dream\n| note3     = extended promo\n| title4    = If It Wasn't for the Nights\n| note4     = ''Mike Yarwood Christmas Show'', BBC\n| title5    = Chiquitita\n| note5     = ''Christmas Snowtime Special'', BBC\n| title6    = ''Bj\u00f6rn & Benny Interview''\n| note6     = ''[[Multi-Coloured Swap Shop]]'', BBC\n| title7    = ''Greatest Hits Vol. 2''\n| note7     = television commercial I\n| title8    = ''Greatest Hits Vol. 2''\n| note8    = television commercial II\n| title9   = International sleeve gallery\n}}\n'''Notes:'''\n{{ref|a|[a]}} mislabeled as 4:12.\n\n==Personnel==\n* [[Agnetha F\u00e4ltskog]] \u2013 [[Singing|lead vocals]] {{small|(1, 8, 10, 13)}}, co-lead vocals {{small|(2, 4, 7, 11, 12, 14)}} backing vocals\n* [[Frida Lyngstad|Anni-Frid Lyngstad]] \u2013 lead vocals {{small|(3, 5, 9, 14)}}, co-lead vocals {{small|(2, 4, 7, 11, 12, 14)}}, backing vocals\n* [[Bj\u00f6rn Ulvaeus]] \u2013 [[banjo]], [[guitar]], lead vocals {{small|(6, 11)}}, backing vocals\n* [[Benny Andersson]] \u2013 [[synthesizer]], [[Keyboard instrument|keyboards]], co-lead vocals {{small|(11)}}, backing vocals<ref>{{cite web|title= Who sings this song? |website= ABBA Omnibus |accessdate= 9 September 2018 |url= http://www.abbaomnibus.net/songs/whosings.htm}}</ref>\n\n'''Additional musicians'''\n{{div col||colwidth=35em}}\n* Rolf Alex \u2013 [[Drum kit|drums]]\n* [[Ola Brunkert]] \u2013 drums\n* Lars Carlsson \u2013 [[Horn (instrument)|horn]]\n* Anders Eljas \u2013 horn\n* Joe Galdo \u2013 drums\n* [[Malando Gassama]] \u2013 [[Percussion instrument|percussion]]\n* [[Rutger Gunnarsson]] \u2013 [[